com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters
Class Calendar

java.lang.Object
  com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters.Calendar
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class Calendar
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

This class represents a calendar object with all the info it can contains and the operations we can execute over this object, most of them related with CRUD event operations. It is also remarkable that we have methods in order to be able to transform this object into a CalendarEntry object an viceversa

Author:
Sergio Martinez Rodriguez
